Real model: download bge-small-en-v1.5 quantized int8 ONNX from
https://huggingface.co/BAAI/bge-small-en-v1.5 (or the ONNX export at
https://huggingface.co/onnx-community/bge-small-en-v1.5-ONNX) and save as
bge-small-en-v1.5-int8.onnx (without .placeholder suffix). ~33 MB.

When this file is present at assets/models/bge-small-en-v1.5-int8.onnx, the
OnnxEmbedder will load it via ONNX Runtime Mobile (with NNAPI delegate) on
first use and produce real 384-dim BGE-small-en-v1.5 embeddings. Until then,
EmbedderProvider falls back to MockEmbedder (deterministic hash-based 384-dim
embeddings) — see app/src/main/java/com/babymomo/core/memory/OnnxEmbedder.kt
and EmbedderProvider.kt.
